decision_conditions:
Condition : 4 - Prior to commencement of works above ground level details of all the external materials, including samples, of all materials to be used in the construction of the external surfaces of the development hereby permitted have been submitted to and approved in writing by the local planning authority. The samples and details shall include:
 	brickwork (including brick sample panels on-site as appropriate); 
 	cladding materials (including sample panels);
 	window details (manufacturers specifications); and  
 	any other materials/details to be used 
The development shall be carried out in accordance with the approved details and so maintained at all times thereafter.
